{"tid":642941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國戰機又來亂了！這次還這樣挑釁台灣軍...說「你真牛逼，還中華民國呢！」 再嗆說「說你香港國語練好吧...」。","createTime":"2018-04-26T07:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T07:42:02.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c7d1a97f71977ce7286339d3a03384b6f7826c","tid":642941,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"共機又來亂了！這次還這樣挑釁我軍...<br />\n<br />\n2018-04-26 14:06<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國軍機又來亂，這次還嗆我戰管人員！<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果日報》報導，中國軍機今天上午再度闖入我國防空識別區，空軍戰管透過空中無線電廣播要求共軍飛離，沒想到話還沒說完即被對方打斷，嗆聲說「你真牛逼，還中華民國呢！」<br />\n我空軍戰管未理會共軍的挑釁，繼續用廣播喊話，未料對方再嗆說「說你香港國語練好吧...」。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"a973e0ec1884081cc8c24d9566d93dd46478ceda","tid":642941,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"又錯唔晒<br />\n那裡仲有中華民國<br />\n侵侵曾稱呼小英做台灣總統<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f1707dbdc2ff3d4a354e39b3fb410e68d16e5d","tid":642941,"uid":72186,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"未料對方再嗆說「說你香港國語練好吧...」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港的國語是粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c7a19a43d0ef39dd5198517da92424830f1602","tid":642941,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34f1707dbdc2ff3d4a354e39b3fb410e68d16e5d","tid":642941,"uid":72186,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"未料對方再嗆說「說你香港國語練好吧...」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港的國語是粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder